04d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hikingyogi/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hikingyogi</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 25, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have been in IT for 30 years, but I have ZERO experience in designing web sites. I allowed AI to develop my initial site and then edited it to suit my style and needs. However, when I got to the products page, I was totally stuck on how to display our products by category. I researched it and tried to follow all of the instructions but because I have a block design, some of the things that were mentioned were not in the right place or didn\'t exist at all. Over the span of 3 days and multiple people, the members of the forum checked out my site and carefully explained what I would need to do. The final person who helped me even sent a video, which was extremely helpful. I can\'t thank everyone enough for the assistance - even when it felt hopeless, they stuck with me and got it taken care of.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">super</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amigapple/\"><img alt